      <title>咖啡烘焙商 Lavazza 表示，2025 年咖啡价格将继续上涨</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-09/coffee-prices-will-keep-rising-into-2025-roaster-lavazza-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于主要种植区的供应短缺，咖啡价格将持续上涨至 2025 年中期，随着新的森林砍伐法规的实施，欧洲消费者将为咖啡因支付更高的价格。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-09/coffee-prices-will-keep-rising-into-2025-roaster-lavazza-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 09 Jul 2024 17:02:42 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
