      <title>俄罗斯外汇交易目前几乎 100% 以人民币进行</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-09/russia-s-foreign-exchange-trading-is-now-almost-100-in-yuan</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在制裁迫使莫斯科交易所暂停美元和欧元交易后，人民币在俄罗斯外汇市场的份额已达到99.6%。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-09/russia-s-foreign-exchange-trading-is-now-almost-100-in-yuan</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 09 Jul 2024 16:50:31 GMT</pubDate>
