      <title>耶伦为拜登辩护，称其在会议中“极其高效”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-09/yellen-defends-biden-as-extremely-effective-in-meetings</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在众议院听证会上，当被问及总统的精神敏锐度时，财政部长珍妮特·耶伦表示，她的老板乔·拜登在他们都参加的长时间会议中表现得“极其高效”。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-09/yellen-defends-biden-as-extremely-effective-in-meetings</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 09 Jul 2024 16:11:35 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>RTX 即将与 Arcline 达成协议出售其子公司</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-09/rtx-corp-is-said-to-near-deal-to-sell-unit-to-arcline</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，RTX 公司正就将其柯林斯航空航天部门的一个部门出售给私募股权公司 Arcline Investment Management 进行深入谈判。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-09/rtx-corp-is-said-to-near-deal-to-sell-unit-to-arcline</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 09 Jul 2024 15:54:24 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>鲍威尔呼吁提供通胀回落的证据，美国国债价格下跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-09/treasuries-slip-as-powell-calls-for-evidence-of-inflation-s-ebb</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美联储主席杰罗姆·鲍威尔向华盛顿立法者表示，他希望看到更多通胀降温的证据，以实现市场对今年降息的押注，美国国债价格下跌。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-09/treasuries-slip-as-powell-calls-for-evidence-of-inflation-s-ebb</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 09 Jul 2024 15:22:16 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>知情人士称西迪克将出任英国城市事务大臣</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-09/tulip-siddiq-to-be-uk-s-city-minister-person-familiar-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国首相基尔·斯塔默 (Keir Starmer) 将任命图利普·西迪克 (Tulip Siddiq) 为英国金融城大臣，该职位属于财政部，将让她成为监管和倡导关键金融服务行业的核心人物。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-09/tulip-siddiq-to-be-uk-s-city-minister-person-familiar-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 09 Jul 2024 15:01:53 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Bobby Jain 的复杂对冲基金首次亮相，引来众多粉丝和质疑者</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-09/bobby-jain-s-complex-hedge-fund-debut-spawns-fans-and-doubters</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在优雅的 Breakers Palm Beach 度假村内，Bobby Jain 进行了价值数十亿美元的宣传。他的听众是阿布扎比投资局，该局掌管着全球最大的石油公司之一，对 Jain 来说，他是他的新对冲基金的完美客户。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-09/bobby-jain-s-complex-hedge-fund-debut-spawns-fans-and-doubters</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 09 Jul 2024 11:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
